0a%20freelance%20writer%20specializing%20in%20home%20and%20outdoor%20products%2C%20they're%20the%20only%20brand%20offering%20furniture%20that%20incorporates%20heating%20pads%20inside%20outdoor%20furniture%20cushions%20that%20are%20powered%20by%20batteries%2C%20allowing%20users%20to%20place%20the%20sofas%2C%20chairs%2C%20or%20ottomans%20wherever%20they%20want%20on%20their%20patio%20or%20yard.%20Kevin%20Long%20and%20Alex%20Duncan%20co-founded%20the%20Austin-based%20company%20in%202022%2C%20two%20years%20after%20Long%20had%20the%20idea%20of%20heated%20outdoor%20furniture%20during%20Thanksgiving%20in%202020.%20The%20Austin-based%20company%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20from%20building%20a%20prototype%20in%20Duncan's%20living%20room%20to%20the%20sleek%20and%20comfortable%20outdoor%20furniture%20that%20makes%20it%20more%20desirable%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20outside%20in%20chilly%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20weather-resistant%20properties%20and%20five%20different%20heating%20levels%2C%20Outmore%20Living's%20heated%20furniture%20is%20giving%20people%20more%20opportunities%20to%20enjoy%20the%20outdoors%20for%20far%20less%20work%20than%20it%20takes%20to%20start%20a%20fire%20and%20less%20CO2%20emissions%20than%20propane%20heaters%20emit.%20When%20I%20posted%20the%20furniture%20on%20my%20social%20media%2C%20quite%20a%20few%20friends%20reached%20out%20with%20interest.%20Those%20who%20lived%20in%20cooler%20places%2C%20like%20Alaska%2C%20commented%20how%20such%20furniture%20would%20make%20a%20huge%20difference%20in%20their%20lives.%20Among%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-places-buy-outdoor-patio-furniture-online%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20places%20to%20buy%20outdoor%20furniture%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Outmore%20Living%20is%20one%20to%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f10e3a6-35e7-4c72-9d13-423a11d66040%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3C