ving%20calls%20their%20heating%20design%20HeatTech.%20The%20back%20and%20bottom%20cushions%20are%20connected%20by%20locking%20connectors%2C%20which%20are%20linked%20to%20the%20power%20bar%20mount%2C%20located%20on%20the%20underside%20of%20the%20teak%20frame.%20Each%20seat%20has%20a%20port%2C%20which%20the%20power%20bar%20magnetically%20connects%20to.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20built-in%20USB-A%20and%20USB-C%20plug%20to%20charge%20your%20devices..%20While%20the%20power%20bar%20is%20visible%2C%20it%20is%20not%20garishly%20so.%20You're%20able%20to%20set%20your%20furniture%20collection%20anywhere%2C%20no%20power%20outlet%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Outmore%20Living%20improves%20its%20design%20and%20technology%2C%20it%20is%20also%20committed%20to%20sustainability.%20Rather%20than%20needing%20to%20replace%20the%20furniture%20in%20its%20entirety%2C%20the%20teak%20frame%20is%20built%20for%20the%20long%20haul.%20As%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20enhance%20its%20offerings%2C%20you%20may%20find%20yourself%20considering%20upgraded%20HeatTech%2C%20replaceable%20cushions%2C%20and%20other%20accessories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutmore%20Living%20has%20also%20partnered%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Foutmoreliving.com%2Fpages%2Flocations%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshowrooms%20and%20retailers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20several%20states%20to%20allow%20customers%20to%20see%20the%20furniture%20in%20person.%20It%20even%20lists%20the%20coffee%20shops%20and%20hotels%20where%20its%20products%20are%20utilized%20if%20you're%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22852da546-2125-42e1-aade-fcd1e72a6ea4%5C%22%3EOur%20review%20of%20Outmore%20Living%20Heated%20Outdoor%20Furniture%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2241068bb8-4605-4017-856d-616407febeb3%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Delivery%5C%22%3EDelivery%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221861%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Outmore%20Living%20furniture%20being%20delivered%20and%20unboxed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6852f8eb85e81483682c5d6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221396%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20furniture%20arrives%20pre-assembled%2C%20but%20the%20white%20glove%20delivery%20entails%20unboxing%2C%20adding%20the%20cushions%20and%20hauling%20away%20the%20packaging.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOutmore%20Living's%20heated%20furniture%20is%20made%20to%20order%20and%20typically%20ships%20for%20free%20with%20a%20white%20glove%20delivery%20service%20within%202-3%20weeks.%20Unfortunately%2C%20Outmore%20Living%20happened%20to%20be%20changing%20their%20shipping%20carrier%20right%20when%20I%20was%20scheduled%20to%20do%20this%20review%2C%20and%20because%20of%20that%2C%20my%20experience%20with%20delivery%20and%20set%20up%20was%20different%20than%20what%20most%20people%20will%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20my%20furniture%20being%20delivered%2C%20the%20three%20batteries%20were%20shipped%20for%20free%20in%20the%20mail%20to%20my%20house.%20I%20did%20have%20an%20issue%20with%20one%20of%20the%20batteries%20not%20working.%20It%20just%20wouldn't%20turn%20on%2C%20but%20the%20company%20sent%20out%20another%20the%20next%20day%20with%20a%20return%20label%20so%20I%20could%20send%20back%20the%20battery%20for%20inspection.%20Having%20tested%20a%20lot%20of%20products%20in%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20I%20know%20better%20than%20most%20that%20sometimes%20batteries%20just%20don't%20work%2C%20so%20I%20wasn't%20upset%20by%20this%20at%20all.%20It%20can%20happen%20to%20any%20company%2C%20and%20Outmore%20Living%20was%20very%20prompt%20in%20its%20response%20to%20rectify%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20furniture%20delivery%2C%20I%20was%20sent%20notifications%20by%20email%20to%20set%20up%20a%20delivery%20date%20and%20time.%20The%20shipping%20carrier%20also%20gave%20me%20a%20call%2C%20granting%20me%20the%20opportunity%20to%20choose%20an%20earlier%20date%20than%20what%20I%20was%20provided%20in%20the%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20delivery%20day%2C%20two%20men%20arrived%20with%20the%20Solerno%20loveseat%20and%20lounge%20chair.%20They%20placed%20the%20pre-assembled%20furniture%20on%20my%20back%20porch%2C%20connected%20the%20cushions%2C%20and%20took%20away%20all%20the%20packaging.%20The%20entire%20delivery%20lasted%20less%20than%2020%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c0f07dfc-7674-4047-ac37-6d43c0e6ffb8%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Comfort%5C%22%3EComfort%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221861%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Plate%20of%20tea%20and%20avocado%20toast%20placed%20on%20Outmore%20Living%20heated%20loveseat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6852f888f748d8c055f3f6e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221396%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20memory%20foam%20cushions%20are%20comfortable%20to%20sit%20on.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cushions%20on%20the%20Solerno%20lounge%20chair%20and%20loveseat%20are%20very%20comfortable.%20Made%20of%20memory%20foam%20and%20covered%20in%20Sunbrella%20fabric%2C%20the%20cushions%20are%20a%20delight%20to%20sit%20on.%20The%20fabric%20is%20smooth%20and%20comfortable%20on%20my%20skin%2C%20while%20the%20cushions%20have%20a%20medium%20firm%20feel%2C%20which%20means%20they're%20supportive%20without%20being%20hard%20or%20uncomfortable.%20I%20sink%20slightly%20in%2C%20but%20not%20too%20much%20to%20make%20me%20think%20the%20memory%20foam%20will%20break%20down%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20how%20wide%20the%20lounge%20chair%20is%2C%20making%20it%20a%20good%20option%20for%20people%20of%20various%20sizes.%20The%202-seat%20sofa%20and%20the%20lounge%20chair%20are%20deep%20with%20tall%20backs%20for%20ultimate%20support.%20Even%20though%20they're%20deep%2C%20I%20can%20still%20place%20my%20feet%20on%20the%20ground%20when%20my%20backside%20is%20set%20against%20the%20back%20cushion%20(I'm%205'5%26quot%3B%20for%20reference).%20Sometimes%2C%20I'll%20lie%20on%20the%20loveseat%20with%20my%20head%20leaning%20against%20one%20arm%20of%20the%20sofa%20and%20my%20feet%20hanging%20over%20the%20opposite%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e9007e54-ef2d-47e8-9b8a-5af1bb7b044d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Heating%5C%22%3EHeating%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221861%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Heating%20controls%20on%20the%20Outmore%20Living%20furniture%20set%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6852f80585e81483682c5d3c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221396%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20removable%20batteries%20provided%20up%20to%20seven%20hours%20of%20heat%20across%20five%20temperature%20settings%20ranging%20from%2085%C2%B0F%20to%20120%C2%B0F.%20The%20power%20bank%20indicates%20battery%20level%20and%20your%20selected%20heat%20setting.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20you%20can%20use%20Outmore%20Living's%20furniture%20year-round%2C%20its%20heating%20feature%20is%20what%20makes%20it%20unique.%20Its%20HeatTech%20system%20combines%20a%20battery%20heating%20pad%20within%20the%20cushions%20to%20create%20heated%20outdoor%20furniture.%20A%20power%20bar%20connects%20to%20the%20underside%20of%20the%20teak%20frame%20with%20magnets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20five%20heating%20levels%20(85%C2%B0F%20to%20120%C2%B0F)%2C%20adjusted%20via%20arrows%20on%20the%20power%20bar.%20The%20cushion%20grows%20warm%20within%2015-60%20seconds%20(though%20I%20usually%20felt%20the%20cushion%20grow%20warm%20within%2015-20%20seconds).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20heated%20pad%20does%20not%20stretch%20to%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20cushion%2C%20though%20it's%20quite%20large%20and%20centered%20along%20the%20back%20and%20bottom%20cushion.%20The%20highest%20heating%20level%20is%20toasty.%20I'd%20suggest%20it%20for%20deep%20winter%20and%20the%20fourth%20highest%20heating%20level%20for%20cool%20days%20in%20the%20fall%20or%20spring.%20Because%20I%20tested%20the%20furniture%20in%20May%2C%20I%20usually%20used%20the%20first%2C%20second%2C%20or%20third%20heating%20level%20in%20the%20early%20mornings%20or%20evenings%20when%20it%20was%20breezy%20but%20not%20cold.%20I%20know%20I'll%20find%20daily%20use%20of%20this%20sofa%20come%20fall%20and%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20power%20bars%20are%20marketed%20to%20last%20up%20to%2010%20hours%2C%20I%20experienced%20a%20range.%20At%20the%20highest%20heat%20setting%2C%20the%20power%20bar%20lasted%20two%20hours%20and%20five%20minutes.%20Another%20time%2C%20just%2050%20minutes%2C%20which%20transparently%20is%20not%20the%20longest%20time%2C%20but%20it's%20enough%20to%20enjoy%20a%20coffee%20in%20the%20morning%20or%20maybe%20a%20whisky%20in%20the%20evening.%20This%20was%20after%20the%20battery%20had%20been%20charged%20days%20earlier%20and%20sat%20in%20my%20house%20fully%20charged%20until%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20test%20the%20heat%20again.%20There's%20little%20difference%20between%20the%20fourth%20and%20fifth%20heating%20levels%2C%20so%20to%20get%20some%20longer%20use%20out%20of%20the%20power%20bar%2C%20I'd%20suggest%20using%20the%20fourth%20heating%20level%20if%20it's%20particularly%20cold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20lowest%20heat%20setting%2C%20the%20battery%20lasted%20seven%20hours%20and%2015%20minutes%20one%20time%20and%20two%20hours%20and%2045%20minutes%20another%20time.%20I%20suspect%20you'll%20get%20the%20best%20use%20out%20of%20the%20battery%20if%20you%20charge%20the%20power%20bar%20and%20use%20it%20right%20away.%20Leave%20it%20sitting%20for%20a%20day%20or%20two%2C%20and%20it's%20likely%20that%20the%20charge%20goes%20down%20even%20if%20it%20reads%20as%20fully%20charged.%20To%20verify%20this%20theory%2C%20I%20charged%20a%20power%20bar%20and%20used%20it%20the%20next%20day%2C%20only%20for%20it%20to%20last%20six%20hours%20and%2015%20minutes%20on%20the%20lowest%20heating%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharging%20all%20three%20batteries%20takes%20about%206%20hours%20and%2045%20minutes.%20Outmore%20includes%20a%20cord%20that%20can%20charge%20them%20simultaneously%2C%20or%20you%20can%20use%20your%20own%20USB-A%20or%20USB-C%20cables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20have%20a%20bit%20of%20an%20issue%20with%20the%20heating%20capabilities.%20Upon%20first%20testing%2C%20one%20cushion%20initially%20stopped%20heating%20after%2030%20minutes%20but%20worked%20again%20after%20moving%20the%20cushions%20around%20and%20reconnecting.%20Later%2C%20the%20sofa's%20power%20bars%20paused%20with%20no%20warning%20%E2%80%94%20lights%20froze%20and%20heat%20stopped.%20Swapping%20the%20bars%20helped%20one%20side%2C%20but%20the%20other%20didn't%20resume%20heating.%20The%20chair's%20power%20bar%20also%20shut%20off%20unexpectedly%20but%20worked%20again%20after%20restarting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%20why%20I%20experienced%20these%20glitches%20at%20some%20points%20during%20testing%20and%20not%20during%20others.%20As%20far%20as%20I%20can%20tell%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20sitting%20on%20the%20furniture%20for%20the%20power%20bar%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20glitches%20are%20not%20great%2C%20the%20likelihood%20of%20my%20sitting%20on%20this%20furniture%20for%20more%20than%20three%20hours%20at%20a%20time%20is%20slim%2C%20and%20I'm%20confident%20the%20battery%20power%20can%20last%20for%20at%20least%20three%20hours%20at%20the%20third%20and%20fourth%20heat%20levels.%20Outmore%20Living%20responded%20quickly%20to%20my%20issues%2C%20and%20I%20expect%20continued%20improvements%20with%20future%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2200e76e4c-64e8-4959-9d8f-a7c0373c308d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Durability%5C%22%3EDurability%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20three%20weeks%20of%20testing%20the%20Solerno%202-seat%20sofa%20and%20chair%20on%20my%20uncovered%20porch%20during%20a%20particularly%20rainy%20Texas%20May%2C%20I've%20gotten%20a%20good%20sense%20of%20their%20durability.%20I%20covered%20them%20with%20a%20tarp%20to%20protect%20them%20when%20not%20in%20use%2C%20though%20some%20moisture%20and%20dirt%20still%20got%20through.%20Thankfully%2C%20the%20cushions%20dried%20quickly%20and%20were%20easy%20to%20clean%2C%20as%20was%20the%20teak%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FSC-certified%20teak%20feels%20sturdy%20and%2C%20with%20proper%20care%2C%20could%20last%20decades.%20The%20medium-firm%20memory%20foam%20cushions%20also%20appear%20well-made%2C%20though%20like%20all%20foam%2C%20their%20longevity%20will%20depend%20on%20usage%20and%20care.%20I%20plan%20to%20store%20the%20cushions%20when%20not%20in%20use%20to%20extend%20their%20life.%20The%20Sunbrella%20fabric%20might%20be%20resistant%20to%20water%2C%20stains%2C%20and%20UV%20rays%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20water%20won't%20be%20absorbed%20by%20the%20cushions%2C%20which%20could%20affect%20the%20memory%20foam%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20HeatTech%20is%20impressive%2C%20its%20long-term%20durability%20is%20unclear.%20The%20power%20bars%20and%20HeatTech%20pads%20have%20relatively%20short%20warranties%20(one%20and%20two%20years)%2C%20so%20I'm%20storing%20the%20power%20bars%20indoors%20when%20not%20in%20use%20for%20extra%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2294b5c1b2-bec4-4022-992c-8d29096f6ebb%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Returns%20and%20warranty%5C%22%3EReturns%20and%20warranty%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOutmore%20Living%20allows%20returns%20within%2045%20days.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20a%2020%25%20return%20fee%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20shipping.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20Solerno%20Heated%202-Seat%20sofa%20set%20return%20fee%20would%20be%20%241%2C750%20(which%20is%2020%25%20of%20its%20%248%2C750%20price%20tag).%20While%20steep%2C%20the%20return%20fee%20is%20understandable%20for%20made-to-order%20furniture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDifferent%20parts%20of%20the%20furniture%20have%20different%20warranties.%20The%20power%20bars%20only%20have%20a%20one-year%20warranty%2C%20while%20the%20HeatTech%20heating%20pads%20are%20covered%20under%20a%202-year%20warranty.%20The%20teak%20frames%20are%20covered%20under%20a%203-year%20warranty%2C%20while%20the%20cushion%20covers%20and%20foam%20inserts%20have%20a%205-year%20warranty.%20The%20teak%20frame%20and%20cover%20warranties%20are%20average%2C%20if%20not%20better%2C%20than%20most%20warranties%20for%20outdoor%20furniture.%20However%2C%20I%20would%20prefer%20a%20longer%20warranty%20for%20the%20power%20bars%20and%20heating%20pads%2C%20only%20because%20technology%20such%20as%20these%20can%20be%20finicky%2C%20and%20I%20think%20it%20would%20be%20nice%20to%20have%20them%20covered%20for%20much%20longer%20than%20one%20to%20two%20years.%20For%20reference%2C%20if%20a%20power%20bar%20dies%20after%20a%20year%2C%20a%20replacement%20is%20%24400.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2201baf048-ec05-4c13-bf26-e4fde0057f99%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20HeatTech%20technology%20is%20impressive%2C%20customers%20should%20be%20prepared%20that%20the%20battery%20life%20is%20not%20always%20consistent%2C%20and%20glitches%20can%20occur.%20In%20my%20testing%2C%20the%20longest%20a%20power%20bar%20lasted%20was%20a%20little%20over%207%20hours%20on%20the%20lowest%20heat%20setting%20and%20as%20short%20as%2050%20minutes%20on%20the%20highest%20heat%20setting.%20It%20doesn't%20help%20that%20the%20power%20bars%20take%20over%206%20hours%20to%20charge.%20Add%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20power%20bar%20warranty%20is%20only%20one%20year%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20little%20unclear%20how%20durable%20the%20power%20bars%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20appreciate%20that%20Outmore%20Living%20offers%20free%20white%20glove%20delivery%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20return%20the%20product%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20cost%20a%20pretty%20high%20fee.%20In%20fact%2C%20Outmore%20Living%20charges%2020%25%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20product%20plus%20a%20shipping%20fee.%20This%20makes%20sense%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20considering%20that%20their%20furniture%20is%20all%20made%20upon%20ordering%2C%20but%20that%20aside%2C%20you%20should%20probably%20be%20completely%20sure%20of%20your%20purchase%20before%20investing%20in%20this%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f9643655-ade3-467d-91c1-3ac1717f6743%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Polywood%20outdoor%20patio%20furniture%20set%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6852f7e8f748d8c055f3f6ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22975%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPolywood's%20mimics%20the%20look%20of%20teak%20furniture%2C%20but%20is%20made%20with%20durable%20and%20water-resistant%20HDPE%2C%20which%20is%20very%20low%20maintenance%20and%20built%20to%20last.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20other%20brands%20that%20sell%20outdoor%20heated%20furniture%2C%20you'll%20be%20disappointed%20to%20discover%20that%20there%20is%20likely%20only%20one%20other%20company%20with%20a%20similar%20offering.%20Galanter%20%26amp%3B%20Jones'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgalanterandjones.com%2Fcollections%2Fkosmos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKosmos%20Collection%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20very%20modern%20in%20style%20with%20a%20molded%20cast%20stone%20construction%2C%20but%20lacks%20the%20plush%20cushions%20that%20Outmore%20Living%20has.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20plugged%20into%20an%20outlet%20for%20its%20heating%20element%2C%20with%20a%20cord%20that%20ultimately%20limits%20where%20you%20can%20place%20the%20Kosmos%20Chair%20or%20Lounge.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20slightly%20more%20affordable%20than%20Outmore%20Living's%20heated%20furniture%20collection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20you%20can%20always%20enjoy%20h