nd%20build%20momentum%20as%20the%20PC%20refresh%20cycle%20picks%20up%20speed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20staff%20in%20the%20memo%2C%20which%20BI%20has%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClarke%2C%20who%20has%20been%20at%20Dell%20since%201987%20and%20is%20a%20key%20lieutenant%20of%20billionaire%20founder%20Michael%20Dell%2C%20also%20announced%20a%20series%20of%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdell-reorganizes-top-ranks-asks-senior-managers-lead-more-staff-2025-5%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDell%2520is%2520pushing%2520for%2520a%2C20%2520people%2520reporting%2520to%2520them.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleadership%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20told%20staff%20that%20%26quot%3Bmodernizing%20how%20we%20operate%20includes%20fine-tuning%20leader%20roles%20and%20reporting%20lines%20so%20we%20can%20go%20fast%20and%20win.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reorganization%20included%20appointing%20Sam%20Burd%2C%20previously%20the%20president%20of%20CSG%2C%20to%20lead%20Dell's%20corporate%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell%20splits%20its%20business%20into%20two%20units%3A%20CSG%20and%20ISG%2C%20the%20infrastructure%20solutions%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemand%20for%20AI%20is%20driving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdell-business-trends-of-the-year-rto-ai-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egrowth%20in%20the%20ISG%20division%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20develops%20AI%20servers%20%E2%80%94%20ISG%20revenue%20was%20up%2029%25%20in%20Dell's%20last%20full%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20CSG's%20annual%20revenue%20has%20declined%20every%20year%20since%202022%2C%20when%20it%20peaked%20amid%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-layoffs-tech-ceo-pandemic-boom-last-forever-dumb-mistake-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epandemic-era%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20PC%20sales.%20Total%20CSG%20revenue%20was%20%2448.6%20billion%20in%202025%2C%20down%2021%25%20from%20its%202022%20peak%2C%20and%20just%20above%