CEO%20Michael%20Dell%20promoted%20the%20company's%20AI%20PCs%2C%20saying%20they%20deliver%20%26quot%3Blonger%2C%20multi-day%20battery%20life%2C%20smoother%20workflows%2C%20and%20the%20confidence%20that%20you're%20ready%20for%20the%20AI%20era.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20companies%20see%20challenges%20to%20their%20revenue%20and%20market%20share%2C%20as%20Dell%20recently%20has%2C%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20to%20make%20organizational%20changes%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20bring%20new%20ideas%20into%20the%20mix%2C%26quot%3B%20Bob%20Woodward%2C%20the%20president%20and%20chief%20analyst%20at%20Technalysis%20Research%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWoodward%20said%20the%20reorganization%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bsubtle%20rearranging%20of%20the%20chairs%2C%20but%20hopefully%20one%20that%20drives%20the%20kind%20of%20new%20ideas%20Dell%20needs%20to%20reinvigorate%20their%20critical%20PC%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20leadership%20changes%20come%20one%20week%20after%20Dell's%20annual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftell-dell-results-employee-satisfaction-falls-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eemployee%20survey%20results%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20released%20internally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell's%20employee%20satisfaction%20score%20%E2%80%94%20known%20as%20the%20employee%20net%20promoter%20score%2C%20or%20eNPS%20%E2%80%94%20fell%20to%2032%2C%20according%20to%20a%20transcript%20of%20a%20video%20update%20obtained%20by%20BI.%20Amid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdell-employee-numbers-decline-by-25000-since-2023-rto-layoffs-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworkforce%20reductions%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20RTO%20mandates%2C%20the%20eNPS%20has%20declined%20almost%2050%25%20in%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20Jeff%20Clarke's%20full%20memo%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ETeam%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EModernizing%20how%20we%20operate%20includes%20fine-tuning%20leader%20roles%20and%20reporting%20lines%20so%20we%20can%20go%20fast%20and%20win.%20To%20that%20end%2C%20I'm%20making%20a%20few%20changes%20to%20my%20leadership%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EI've%20asked%20Sam%20Burd%20to%20lead%20Corporate%20Strategy.%20Sam%20is%20an%20expert%20strategist%20and%20his%20BU%20leadership%2C%20deep%20market%20knowledge%20and%20consulting%20background%20will%20be%20instrumental%20as%20we%20plan%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EVivek%20Mohindra%2C%20who%20has%20led%20Corporate%20Strategy%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20will%20take%20on%20a%20new%20role%20as%20Special%20Advisor%2C%20working%20directly%20with%20me%20on%20business-critical%20projects.%20I%20am%20grateful%20for%20the%20leadership%20and%20vision%20he%20brought%20to%20the%20Corporate%20Strategy%20Office%20and%20look%20forward%20to%20working%20with%20him%20in%20this%20new%20capacity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EDennis%20Hoffman%20and%20the%20Telecom%20Systems%20Business%20will%20move%20to%20ISG%2C%20with%20Dennis%20joining%20Arthur%20Lewis's%20Leadership%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20now%2C%20I%20will%20take%20on%20the%20day-to-day%20leadership%20of%20CSG.%20This%20will%20help%20accelerate%20decision%20making%20and%20build%20momentum%20as%20the%20PC%20refresh%20cycle%20picks%20up%20speed.%20The%20following%20CSG%20leaders%20will%20report%20directly%20to%20me%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EAlex%20Barretto%20wil%20lead%20an%20expanded%20team%20including%20PC%20Engineering%20and%20Services%2C%20CTO%2C%20Experinece%20Design%20Group%20and%20GOPO.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EChris%20Cowger%20will%20continue%20to%20lead%20Global%20Consumer%20and%20eCommerce%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EBert%20Park%20will%20now%20lead%20Displays%2C%20Docks%2C%20Partner%20Software%20and%20Client%20Peripherals%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EKaren%20Plot