%20Lloyd%20Pearson.%20Most%20mornings%2C%20though%2C%20she%20takes%20long%20walks%20and%20calls%20her%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20time%20I%20find%20myself%20the%20most%20peaceful%20to%20talk%2C%20and%20not%20rushed%20or%20distracted%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20usually%20call%20someone%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20or%20I%20have%20a%20couple%20of%20girlfriends%20I%20know%20are%20up%20early%20and%20could%20talk.%20Then%20I%20get%20my%20business%20calls%20out%20of%20the%20way.%20I%20usually%20walk%20for%20about%20an%20hour%20and%20fifteen%20minutes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20healthy%20staple%20of%20her%20routine%20is%20a%20protein%20shake%20made%20with%20almond%20milk%2C%20chocolate%20Vital%20Proteins%20powder%2C%20a%20scoop%20of%20natural%20peanut%20butter%2C%20Greek%20yogurt%2C%20ice%2C%20and%20occasionally%2C%20a%20frozen%20banana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20try%20to%20make%20the%20best%20choices%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%20but%20not%20beat%20myself%20up%20when%20I%20do%20something%20that%20doesn't%20make%20me%20feel%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20morning%20feeling%20inflamed%20or%20puffy%20or%20tired%2C%20I%20stop%20and%20say%2C%20'OK%2C%20what%20did%20I%20do%20yesterday%3F%20Did%20I%20not%20drink%20enough%20water%3F'%20I%20guess%20it%20would%20be%20called%20intuitive%20wellness.%20Listen%20to%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20healthtech%20advisor%20relies%20on%20iced%20coffee%20and%20Amazon%20Alexa%20to%20start%20her%20day.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222876%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alexa-enabled%20Amazon%20Echo%20smart%20speaker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687e618f85e81483682e5d2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222157%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20general%20view%20of%20an%20Amazon%20Echo%20smart%20speaker.%20Amazon's%20Alexa%20is%20set%20to%20answer%20people's%20health%20queries%20by%20searching%20th