Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20opens%20the%20blinds%2C%20tells%20me%20the%20weather%2C%20runs%20through%20my%20schedule%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSometimes%2C%20I%20play%20a%20mindfulness%20minute%20while%20I'm%20brushing%20my%20teeth.%20Alexa%20allows%20me%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20for%20myself%20and%20be%20educated%20on%20what%20I%20need%20for%20the%20day%2C%20without%20having%20to%20seek%20that%20information%20myself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20really%20key%20to%20Davis'%20productive%20start%20is%20knowing%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20morning%20starts%20the%20night%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20a%20woman%20in%20business%2C%20it's%20chaos.%20You're%20the%20CEO%20of%20your%20franchise%20and%20the%20COO%20of%20your%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20look%20at%20my%20calendar%20the%20night%20before%20and%20say%2C%20'All%20right%2C%20these%20are%20the%20things%20that%20need%20to%20get%20done%20tomorrow%20in%20my%20finite%2024%20hours.%20Let%20me%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20fit%20it%20all%20in%20there.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20managing%20director%20likes%20to%20get%20a%20head%20start%20on%20work%20right%20after%20waking%20up.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222669%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20types%20on%20a%20laptop%2C%20with%20a%20mug%2C%20glasses%2C%20phone%2C%20and%20tablet%20are%20on%20the%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687e934bf748d8c055f5fc60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222002%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPeopleImages%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFatima%20Boolani%2C%2038%2C%20is%20a%20managing%20director%20of%20software%20equity%20research%20at%20Citi%2C%20where%20she%20also%20serves%20as%20cohead%20of%20the%20company's%20US%20software%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20also%20a%20mom%20of%20two%2C%20so%20she%20wakes%20up%20between%206%20a.m.%20and%207%20a.m.%20each%20day%20to%20check%20work%20emails%2C%20news%2C%20research%20reports%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20priority%20is%20to%20get%20a%20head%20start%20on%20the%20day%20such%20that%2C%20while%20I'm%20shifting%20gears%20momentarily%20for%20personal%20and%20family%20reasons%2C%20I%20have%20a%20solid%20footing%20before%20I%20jump%20back%20into%20work%20around%208%20a.m.%20or%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Boolani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20drink%20of%20choice%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bhot%2C%20strong%20cup%20of%20coffee%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Larabars%20are%20her%20go-to%20morning%20snack%20before%20breakfast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20exercise%20is%20a%20key%20ingredient%20to%20her%20success%2C%20Boolani%20said%20she%20prefers%20midday%20workouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20her%2C%20mornings%20are%20about%20using%20a%20limited%20amount%20of%20time%20to%20her%20advantage%20and%20%26quot%3Bfilling%20that%20space%20and%20time%20with%20more%20intention.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20think%20waking%20up%20at%206%20a.m.%20was%20so%20early%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20now%2C%20how%20much%20power%20can%20be%20packed%20in%20that%20punch%20of%20an%20hour%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20with%20two%20children%20%E2%80%94%20is%20really%20awesome.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20CEO%20of%20a%20beauty%20brand%20tests%20her%20new%20products%20while%20working%20out%20each%20morning.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20in%20a%20backpack%20and%20hiking%20clothes%20on%20a%20high%20hilltop%20looking%20over%20a%20sunny%20landscape%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a9845843bb77284b9e3e6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERucking%20is%20a%20fancy%20word%20for%20carrying%20a%20backpack%20as%20exercise%2C%20whether%20your%20in%20a%20beautiful%20landscape%20or%20just%20walking%20around%20your%20neighborhood.%3Cp%3EOlga%20Pankova%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-urban-decay-cofounder-wende-zomnir-created-beauty-empire-caliray-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWende%20Zomnir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2057%2C%20has%20spent%20decades%20in%20the%20beauty%20industry.%20She%20co-founded%20Urban%20Decay%20in%201996%2C%20led%20the%20brand%20until%202022%2C%20and%20then%20launched%20her%20beauty%20line%20Caliray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%20in%20her%20career%2C%20she%20wakes%20up%20between%205%20a.m.%20and%206%20a.m.%20each%20day%20and%20instantly%20drinks%2020%20ounces%20of%20water.%20Her%20second%20morning%20drink%20is%20coffee%20or%20coconut%20water%20with%20some%20protein%20powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20chooses%20the%20latter%20on%20days%20that%20she%20exercises%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vital%20aspects%20of%20her%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20lift%2C%20practice%20yoga%2C%20play%20tennis%2C%20or%20go%20rucking%20in%20the%20soft%20sand%20most%20mornings%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20playing%20beach%20volleyball%2C%20surfing%2C%20snowboarding%2C%20riding%20my%20bike%20%E2%80%94%20I%20like%20to%20move!%20And%20I%20test%20out%20makeup%20formulas%20I'm%20working%20on%20while%20I%20do%20it%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZomnir%20said%20waking%20up%20early%20and%20jumping%20into%20physical%20activities%20helps%20her%20focus%20on%20her%20role%20as%20CEO%20and%20as%20a%20leader%20of%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20thinking%20about%20when%20I'm%20going%20to%20squeeze%20my%20workout%20in%20later%20in%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BPhysical%20activity%20is%20my%20drug%20of%20choice%2C%20so%20I%20work%20better%20when%20I've%20worked%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20my%20kids%20got%20older%2C%20they%20needed%20me%20less%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20so%20I%20was%20able%20to%20shift%20from%20afternoon%20workouts%20to%20the%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BMaking%20adjustments%20that%20sync%20with%20the%20life%20stages%20of%20my%20family%20and%20being%20willing%20to%20optimize%20my%20routine%20has%20made%20the%20biggest%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20fintech%20communications%20CEO%20says%20dance%20breaks%20are%20essential.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224263%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20mom%20dances%20with%20two%20kids%20outside.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687f914d85e81483682e6c72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223197%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKNSY%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGrace%20Keith%20Rodriguez%2C%2040%2C%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Caliber%20Corporate%20Advisers%2C%20a%20fintech%20communications%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20gets%20the%20most%20done%20when%20she%20wakes%20up%20around%205%3A30%20a.m.%20That%20gives%20her%20time%20to%20shower%2C%20get%20dressed%2C%20brew%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%20(from%20Little%20Seed%20Coffee%20Roasters%2C%20a%20company%20founded%20by%20her%20sister%20and%20brother-in-law)%2C%20and%20read%20the%20news%20from%20her%20front%20porch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20she%20can%20enjoy%20one%20of%20the%20most%20special%20parts%20of%20her%20mornings%3A%20a%20dance%20party%20with%20her%20two%20children.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20shakes%20the%20sillies%20out%20and%20gets%20you%20through%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20no%20cold%20plunge%2C%20but%20it%20sort%20of%20has%20the%20same%20effect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeith%20Rodriguez's%20job%20also%20involves%20a%20lot%20of%20travel%2C%20so%20her%20routine%20changes%20slightly%20when%20she's%20on%20the%20road.%20Namely%2C%20she%20likes%20to%20take%20long%20walks%20around%20the%20city%20she's%20visiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20rather%20do%20that%20than%20sit%20in%20the%20hotel%20gym%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20to%20get%20out%20and%20see%20the%20city%2C%20because%20you%20usually%20don't%20get%20an%20opportunity%20to%20do%20that%20at%20conferences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20where%20she%20is%2C%20though%2C%20she%20says%20her%20children%20have%20changed%20how%20she%20starts%20her%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKids%20have%20made%20me%20realize%20how%20important%20routine%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Keith%20Rodriguez%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20always%20known%20that%2C%20but%20it%20just%20makes%20it%20so%20obvious%20that%20you%20can't%20ignore%20it.%20When%20you%20start%20the%20day%20on%20the%20right%20foot%2C%20it's%20really%20important%20for%20them%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20chief%20marketing%20and%20impact%20officer%20listens%20to%20inspirational%20audio%20clips.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225304%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20wearing%20an%20orange%20tank%20top%20and%20blue%20jeans%20scrolls%20on%20her%20phone.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687fa50c85e81483682e6e9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223978%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJuanma%20Hache%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESad%C3%A9%20Muhammad%2C%2034%2C%20is%20Time%20Magazine's%20CMO.%20She%20usually%20checks%20her%20phone%20first%20thing%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20but%20doesn't%20scroll%20on%20social%20media.%20Instead%2C%20she%20opens%20her%20Notes%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20bunch%20of%20affirmations%20for%20different%20categories%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BBased%20on%20what%20I'm%20feeling%20that%20day%2C%20whether%20it's%20personal%2C%20career%2C%20fitness%2C%20etc.%2C%20I'll%20lean%20into%20what%20I%20need%20to%20fill%20me%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuhammad%20also%20reviews%20a%20list%20of%20personal%20goals%20to%20monitor%20her%20progress%20and%20listens%20to%2010-minute%20inspirational%20audios%20on%20the%20entrepreneur-focused%20app%20Alux.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20breakfast%20changes%20day-to-day%2C%20though%20she%20usually%20drinks%20water%20with%20lemon%20in%20the%20mornings.%20Her%20early%20workouts%20also%20vary%2C%20but%20she%20particularly%20enjoys%20strength%20training%20and%20morning%20walks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWalking%20is%20my%20favorite%20physical%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20to%20go%20for%20a%20long%20walk%20in%20the%20park%20or%20through%20my%20neighborhood%2C%20and%20I'm%20either%20listening%20to%20an%20audiobook%2C%20some%20music%2C%20or%20I'm%20on%20a%20call.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Muhammad%2C%20this%20flexible%20routine%20not%20only%20sets%20her%20day%20at%20a%20good%20pace%20but%20also%20allows%20her%20to%20focus%20on%20herself%20and%20her%20toddler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20want%20the%20chance%20to%20be%20present%20with%20him%20when%20he%20wakes%20up%2C%20but%20also%20to%20be%20present%20with%20myself%20and%20have%20some%20me%20time%2C%20I%20need%20to%20be%20up%20between%205%20and%207%20a.m.%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20skincare%20brand%20founder%20says%20lemon%20water%20and%20her%20personal%20trainer%20are%20her%20two%20constants.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221654%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20pours%20a%20glass%20of%20water%20from%20a%20jar%20filled%20with%20lemons%20and%20limes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687faa8985e81483682e6fbe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221241%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Ezeynep%26amp%3Bugur%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20Piper%2C%2043%2C%20is%20a%20therapist%2C%20mother%20of%20two%2C%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20skincare%20brand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsaintcrewe.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESaint%20Crewe%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20most%20of%20the%20year%2C%20she%20gets%20up%20around%206%3A15%20a.m.%20to%20wake%20her%208-y