0Keenan%20Austin%20Reed%2C%20the%20president%20of%20tech%20policy%20think%20tank%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeneral-catalyst-hemant-taneja-redefine-venture-capital-baffling-industry-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Catalyst%20Institute%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20CEO%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebipartisan%20lobbying%20firm%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAlpine%20Group%2C%20respectively%2C%20were%20both%20approached%20about%20joining%20the%20committee%20months%20before%20Ned's%20Club%20opened.%20Both%20Carlson%20and%20Reed%20knew%20members%20of%20the%20committee%20beforehand%20since%20DC%20is%2C%20as%20Carlson%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20big%20small%20town.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlson%20described%20the%20committee%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcustomer%20advisory%20group.%26quot%3B%20Club%20leaders%20guide%20the%20quarterly%20meetings%2C%20which%20often%20take%20place%20over%20dinner.%20In%20the%20months%20since%20opening%2C%20the%20meetings%20have%20focused%20more%20on%20programming%20than%20recruiting%20members%2C%20Carlson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReed%20told%20BI%20that%20committee%20members%20aren't%20paid%20but%20get%20a%20free%20standard%20membership%20to%20the%20club.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221964%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ned's%20Club%20bar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6881559885e81483682e9146%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221478%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20committee%20seeks%20to%20maintain%20a%20balance%20across%20categories.%3Cp%3EFrank%20Frances%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aa8a78e9-acb1-421f-b2a3-67cdee226454%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Ned's%20Club%20is%20%E2%80%94%20and%20isn't%20%E2%80%94%20looking%20for%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBanner%20described%20member%20curation%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bart%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20the%20committee%20goes%20beyond%20pure%20dem