www.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-bubble-rob-arnott-tech-ai-magnificent-seven-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERob%20Arnott%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Research%20Affiliates%20and%20the%20sort%20of%20godfather%20of%20alternative%20stock-market%20indexing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20telling%20him%20about%20a%20recent%20story%20I%20wrote%20for%20younger%20investors%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-in-stocks-etfs-how-much-to-buy-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehow%20much%20of%20their%20portfolio%20they%20should%20have%20in%20ETFs%20versus%20individual%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20takeaway%20from%20the%20story%2C%20based%20on%20chats%20with%20four%20financial%20professionals%2C%20was%20that%20retail%20investors%20should%20simply%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20idea%20of%20stock%20picking%20altogether%20and%20have%20virtually%20all%20of%20their%20equity%20holdings%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-invest-in-index-funds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eindex%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20competition%2C%20they%20said%2C%20is%20too%20steep%2C%20and%20the%20necessary%20research%20takes%20too%20much%20time.%20Plus%2C%20even%20the%20pros%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20beating%20the%20market%3B%20just%2015%25%20of%20funds%20beat%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20over%20the%20last%2015%20years%2C%20according%20to%20SPIVA%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArnott%20said%20it%20wasn't%20bad%20advice.%20But%20never%20one%20to%20go%20completely%20with%20the%20consensus%2C%20he%20also%20pushed%20back%20and%20made%20the%20case%20for%20why%20young%20investors%20should%20actually%20have%20a%20go%20at%20stock%20selection%20with%20part%20of%20their%20portfolio%20if%20they%20want%20to%20%E2%80%94%20not%20for%20the%20potential%20returns%20but%20for%20the%20learning%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20should%20dabble%20a%20li