%20green%20jobs%20to%20replace%20the%20coal%20workforce.%20Therefore%2C%20policies%20must%20support%20alternative%20livelihood%20options%20that%20are%20rooted%20in%20local%20contexts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20should%20also%20target%20deployment%20of%20future%20projects%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Kisan%20Urja%20Suraksha%20evam%20Utthan%20Mahabhiyan%20(PM-KUSUM)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20scale%20up%20agri-photovoltaics%20in%20the%20fossil-fuel-intensive%20districts%20of%20Jharkhand%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20This%20can%20help%20in%20creating%20new%20livelihood%20avenues%20for%20both%20skilled%20and%20semi-skilled%20rural%20youth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20solarisation%20initiative%20in%20the%20agriculture%20sector%20should%20be%20linked%20to%20skilling%20and%20local%20manufacturing.%20As%20per%20a%202023%20study%2C%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20solarisation%20initiative%20could%20generate%20over%201%20million%20jobs%20in%20installation%2C%20sales%2C%20and%20maintenance%20across%20rural%20India.%20The%20government%20should%20create%20district-level%20skilling%20programmes%20linked%20to%20solar%20installation%2C%20pump%20repair%2C%20and%20energy%20entrepreneurship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20reskilling%20is%20insufficient%20if%20jobs%20remain%20informal%2C%20precarious%2C%20or%20unsafe.%20Policies%20must%20mandate%20job%20quality%20standards%20that%20focus%20on%20aspects%20such%20as%20social%20security%20and%20occupational%20safety.%20These%20safeguards%20should%20be%20embedded%20into%20agreements%20negotiated%20at%20the%20time%20of%20plant%2Fmine%20closure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Enact%20legal%20safeguards%20for%20fossil%20fuel%20workers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20India%20has%20more%20than%202%20million%20workers%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20employed%20in%20the%20coal%20sector%2C%20it%20lacks%20statutory%20safeguards%20for%20workers%20w