thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753410040-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-475900%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESetting%20up%20solar%20and%20battery%20manufacturing%20in%20coal%20belts%20can%20replace%20lost%20jobs%20and%20boost%20local%20economies.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20government%20must%20design%20region-specific%20just%20transition%20packages%20that%20go%20beyond%20only%20compensation.%20These%20should%20include%20plans%20for%20economic%20diversification%2C%20job%20creation%2C%20and%20infrastructure%20development.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20most%20solar%20module%20and%20battery%20manufacturing%20currently%20concentrated%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Telangana%2C%20priority%20should%20be%20given%20to%20setting%20up%20such%20manufacturing%20units%20in%20high-transition%20regions.%20This%20not%20only%20replaces%20lost%20employment%20but%20also%20builds%20future-ready%20ecosystems%20in%20the%20same%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Enable%20women%20and%20marginalised%20workers%20in%20energy%20transitions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20transition%20to%20be%20just%2C%20it%20must%20be%20gender%20neutral.%20However%2C%20studies%20show%20that%20women%20hold%20less%20than%2011%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20RE%20jobs.%20Skilling%20programmes%20under%20Skill%20India%20and%20National%20Skill%20Development%20Corporation%20(NSDC)%20should%20include%20gender%20quotas%20and%20training%20in%20distributed%20RE%2C%20EV%20maintenance%2C%20and%20green%20construction%2C%20targeting%20rural%20women%2C%20marginalised%20workers%2C%20and%20informal%20sector%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Ensure%20fair%20and%20inclusive%20land%20use%20for%20the%20energy%20transition%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELand%20plays%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20clean%20energy%20transition%2C%20yet%20it%20often%20receives%20little%20attention%20in%20policy%20discussions.%20Large-scale%20RE%20projects%20and%20the%20closure%20of%20coal%20mines%20both%20require%20significant%20land%20use%20changes%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20displacement%2C%20loss%20of%20livelihoods%2C%20and%20conflict%2C%20especially%20in%20tribal%20and%20forest%20areas.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753410144.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Repurposing%20degraded%20coal%20mine%20land%20for%20solar%20parks%20can%20align%20energy%20and%20local%20development%20needs.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753410144.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753410144-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753410144-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753410144-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753410144-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-475902%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepurposing%20degraded%20coal%20mine%20land%20for%20solar%20parks%20can%20align%20energy%20and%20local%20development%20needs.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20just%20transition%20must%20therefore%20ensure%20fair%20land%20practices%2C%20including%20community%20consent%2C%20compensation%2C%20and%20recognition%20of%20informal%20land%20rights.%20Repurposing%20degraded%20coal%20mine%20land%20for%20solar%20parks%20or%20community%20projects%20can%20support%20both%20energy%20and%20local%20development.%20To%20avoid%20land-related%20conflicts%2C%20India%20needs%20an%20integrated%20land%20use%20framework%20that%20balances%20clean%20energy%20expansion%20with%20social%20equity%2C%20ecological%20restoration%2C%20and%20food%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Redirect%20coal%20cess%20revenue%20towards%20transition%20funds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Clean%20Energy%20Cess%20(popularly%20called%20the%20coal%20cess)%20was%20introduced%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20in%202010%20under%20the%20Finance%20Act%20to%20tax%20coal%20production%20and%20imports%2C%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20financing%20clean%20energy%20and%20environmental%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202010%2C%20India%20has%20collected%20over%20INR%201.25%20lakh%20crore%20under%20the%20coal%20cess%20(INR%20400%2Ftonne).%20According%20to%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20of%20India%20(CAG)%20report%2C%20only%20INR%2029%2C645%20crore%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20National%20Clean%20Energy%20Fund%20(NCEF)%2C%20of%20which%20INR%2015%2C911%20crore%2C%20or%20~12%25%20of%20the%20total%2C%20was%20disbursed%20for%20clean%20energy%20projects.%20Thus%2C%20a%20portion%20of%20this%20fund%20can%20be%20reinstated%20to%20support%20worker%20compensation%2C%20skill%20development%2C%20and%20community%20initiatives%20in%20coal%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20Embed%20just%20transition%20metrics%20in%20environment%2C%20social%20and%20governance%20(ESG)%20and%20finance%20norms%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20green%20finance%20in%20India%20is%20growing%2C%20with%20USD%2046%20billion%20in%20green%20bonds%20issued%20as%20of%202024%2C%20ESG%20disclosures%20and%20reporting%20often%20miss%20just%20transition%20indicators%20(e.g.%2C%20employment%20shifts%20and%20local%20economic%20benefits).%20Regulators%20should%20mandate%20Business%20Responsibility%20and%20Sustainability%20Reporting%20to%20include%20metrics%20for%20a%20just%20transition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20transition%20lending%20should%20be%20prioritised%20for%20affected%20micro%2C%20small%2C%20and%20medium-sized%20enterprises%20(MSMEs)%20and%20their%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E9.%20Create%20an%20Authority%20at%20the%20National%20Level%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransition%20responsibility%20is%20currently%20fragmented%20across%20ministries%E2%80%94coal%2C%20labour%2C%20environment%2C%20and%20power.%20A%20national-level%20authority%2C%20with%20legal%20mandate%2C%20coordination%20powers%2C%20and%20representation%20from%20all%20regions%2C%20can%20integrate%20labour%20reskilling%2C%20environmental%20remediation%2C%20and%20regional%20development.%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20Presidential%20Climate%20Commission%20and%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20Coal%20Commission%20provide%20institutional%20blueprints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EConclusion%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20advances%20its%20clean%20energy%20goals%2C%20people%20and%20regions%20most%20affected%20by%20this%20shift%20should%20not%20be%20ignored.%20With%20millions%20of%20workers%20and%20entire%20communities%20depending%20on%20fossil%20fuels%20for%20their%20livelihoods%2C%20simply%20replacing%20coal%20with%20renewables%20without%20addressing%20their%20needs%20would%20deepen%20inequality.%20A%20fair%20transition%20means%20planning%20early%2C%20investing%20in%20reskilling%2C%20supporting%20local%20economies%2C%20ensuring%20job%20security%2C%20and%20making%20space%20for%20women%20and%20marginalised%20groups%20in%20the%20clean%20energy%20workforce.%20With%20the%20right%20policies%20and%20a%20people-first%20approach%2C%20India%20can%20lead%20the%20green%20future%20that%20is%20also%20just%20and%20inclusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753410600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.th