20as%20good%20as%20the%20soil%20from%20which%20the%20mud%20is%20sourced.%20So%2C%20Raghav%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CArchitects%20should%20ideally%20look%20for%20soil%20that%20has%20the%20right%20balance%20of%20clay%20and%20sand.%20Before%20building%20with%20mud%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20essential%20to%20test%20the%20soil.%20If%20the%20soil%20has%20too%20much%20clay%2C%20it%20may%20crack%20as%20it%20dries%3B%20adding%20sand%20helps%20balance%20that%20and%20improve%20workability.%20If%20it%E2%80%99s%20too%20sandy%2C%20the%20mix%20won%E2%80%99t%20hold%20together%20well%3B%20adding%20more%20clay%20brings%20cohesion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20advises%20paying%20attention%20to%20the%20layer%20thickness%20and%20drying%20times.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F316563%2Ftamil-nadu-sustsainable-home-with-plastic-bottles-and-mud-chuzi-vinu-daniel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMud%20construction%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20slower%2C%20seasonal%20process%20that%20calls%20for%20patience.%20It%20dries%20more%20slowly%20in%20winter%20compared%20to%20summer.%20Each%20layer%20needs%20time%20to%20dry%20and%20settle%20before%20the%20next%20is%20added.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20significant%20challenge%2C%20Aishwarya%20points%20out%2C%20is%20finding%20skilled%20artisans%20familiar%20with%20these%20techniques.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20local%20workers%20can%20be%20trained%20in%20natural%20building%20and%20plastering.%20It%20not%20only%20ensures%20quality%20execution%2C%20but%20also%20empowers%20the%20local%20workforce%2C%20creates%20jobs%2C%20and%20boosts%20the%20local%20economy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reasons.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Terracotta%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20biophilic%20design%20is%20what%20the%20architects%20at%20Venkataramanan%20Associates%20were%20going%20for%20when%20they%20designed%20The%20Earth%20Centre%20in%20Bengalur