is%20experiment%20on%20his%2060-acre%20farm%2C%20constructing%20simple%20yet%20effective%20pits%20layered%20with%20stones%2C%20gravel%2C%20and%20sand%20to%20capture%20rainwater%20and%20recharge%20groundwater.%20The%20results%20were%20immediate%3A%20wells%20that%20once%20dried%20up%20by%20December%20now%20brim%20with%20water%2C%20fields%20became%20more%20fertile%2C%20and%20orchards%20flourished%20where%20there%20had%20once%20been%20barren%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20edge%20of%20my%20fields%20in%20Watur%20village%2C%20where%20rainwater%20used%20to%20collect%2C%20I%20began%20laying%20recharge%20pits%20in%20March%20and%20April.%20Every%20acre%20had%20one%20soak%20pit%2C%20so%20I%20installed%20six%20in%20total.%20When%20the%20rains%20arrived%20in%20June%202020%20and%20continued%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%2C%20I%20rushed%20to%20the%20fields%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20jumping%20from%20puddle%20to%20puddle%20with%20an%20umbrella%20in%20hand.%20I%20was%20overjoyed%20to%20see%20that%20the%20rainwater%20had%20percolated%20into%20the%20ground.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20998px)%20100vw%2C%20998px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-dugout-soka-pit_11zon-1753180220.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22998%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maharashtra%20JalTara%20groundwater%20recharge%20pits%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-dugout-soka-pit_11zon-1753180220.jpg%20998w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-dugout-soka-pit_11zon-1753180220-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-dugout-soka-pit_11zon-1753180220-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-dugout-soka-pit_11zon-1753180220-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media